<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2806209" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">题云：<br><blockquote>我们自认为自己在做一件功德无量的事情<br></blockquote><br>有道是：<br>猎头生涯每蹉跎，<br>求教知乎当奈何。<br>我到西天问我佛，<br>佛曰：我也没辙。<br><br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/fa6394fa9661fb720883a9b7699fa9b6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="390" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/fa6394fa9661fb720883a9b7699fa9b6_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="390" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/fa6394fa9661fb720883a9b7699fa9b6_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/fa6394fa9661fb720883a9b7699fa9b6_b.jpg">


